'''Madame [[Baronis]]''' was a "harmless" old lady living on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Peekoine]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. When a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] came to her looking for two [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knights]], she had not had any company in several years and so tried to help them as best she could. Although she kept them in her house for over four hours, she yielded them no useful information.

